description:
Danny recaps this week's Vanderpump Rules, which features the OG gang in Miami continuing the bachelor/bachelorette party. The men do some costume work, the ladies go to a strip club, plus Peter plans his Pride. Danny also addresses the Super Bowl, Liv Tyler in 9-1-1 Lonestar, Jessica's book, & JLO and Shakira.


VPR: 7:37ish
